Pressing this button evaluates the expression and prints its result at the bottom of the screen.

```
{
    "text": "Call $alert() with form parameter",
    "print": "$alert(\"You entered: \" & form.text)",
    "widget": "button",
    "schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
            "text": {
                "required": true
            }
        }
    }
}
```
